Package: hexrec
Title: Visualising River Networks as Hexbins
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Charlotte M.",
           family = "Jones-Todd",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cmjonestodd@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1201-2781"))
Description: An R package that visualises river networks as hexbin networks. hexr enables users to add a ggplot2 layer summarising the supplied river network as a hexbin network. In addition, multiple measures can be displayed in a single "segment". 
Depends: R (>= 3.6.3)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3)
